::KitKat::

She groaned a little in the Cr chamber as she woke up.  She looked 
around, but felt disoriented.  She knew it was a CR chamber, but 
didn't know where it was or how she got there.  She closed her eyed 
and tried to remeber what happened.  She remembered the ship and the 
crash. She remembered jumping from the ship, but everything after 
that was a blurr.  She groand as she still found it painful to 
breath.
